USE hahn; pragma yt.InferSchema='1';

SELECT
    purchase_price.ssku as ssku,
    Yson::ConvertToDouble(Yql::Lookup(Yson::ConvertToDict(purchase_price.dict_regular), '2022-01-29')) as purchase_price,
    Yson::ConvertToDouble(Yql::Lookup(Yson::ConvertToDict(purchase_price.dict_promo), '2022-01-29')) as purchase_promo_price,
    Yson::ConvertToDouble(Yql::Lookup(Yson::ConvertToDict(purchase_price.dict_purchase_price), '2022-01-29')) as purchase_result_price,
    sale_price.price as sale_price,
    sale_price.regular_price as regular_price
FROM `/home/market/production/replenishment/order_planning/2022-01-29/intermediate/assortment_prices_dicts`  with inline as purchase_price
    LEFT JOIN `/home/market/production/ir/ultra-controller/supplier_to_market_sku`  with inline as sku_mapping
ON sku_mapping.shop_sku_id = purchase_price.ssku
    LEFT JOIN `/home/market/production/replenishment/prod/sales_dynamics/calculation_steps/beru_offers/beru_offers_2022-01-29`  with inline as sale_price
    ON sale_price.market_sku = sku_mapping.approved_market_sku_id
WHERE sku_mapping.shop_id = 465852
